            <title><![CDATA[日外长吁中国早日释放上月被拘留日本人]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[<div class="figure-media"><img class="img-fluid lazyload" data-src="https://static.zaobao.com/s3fs-public/styles/article_large_full/public/articles/2023/04/02/2023-04-02T055947Z797373140RC2560AYH082RTRMADP3JAPAN-CHINA-VISIT_3.JPG?VersionId=yw3N7ZZ.oKIOMRzAdW2aWnGYaJ0sgKMR&amp;itok=L0tnkMAP" title="日本外长林芳正星期天（4月2日）在中国北京钓鱼台国宾馆，与中国外长秦刚会面。（路透社/共同社）" alt="日本外长林芳正星期天（4月2日）在中国北京钓鱼台国宾馆，与中国外长秦刚会面。（路透社/共同社）" src="https://static.zaobao.com/s3fs-public/styles/article_large_full/public/articles/2023/04/02/2023-04-02T055947Z797373140RC2560AYH082RTRMADP3JAPAN-CHINA-VISIT_3.JPG?VersionId=yw3N7ZZ.oKIOMRzAdW2aWnGYaJ0sgKMR&amp;itok=L0tnkMAP" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div>
